## Kaizen principles reminder

- One improvement per retro — focused beats scattered
- Follow up every retro: was last sprint's improvement implemented?
- Blameless — systems and processes, not people
- Ask "Why?" five times to find root cause, not symptom
- Celebrate what worked — reinforce good habits
